extendedInfo.description: Do you think you know everything about acid bases? Try our new app Acid Base Quiz !Acid Base Quiz is a game where you have to choose wright answers to above-listed questions.Put you knowledge of acids and bases to the test with this fun science quiz. How much do you know about sulfuric acid, sodium hydroxide, litmus paper and pH levels?Acid Base Quiz will test your knowledge of chemistry. Choose right answer will open the next level.-No ads.-Free app.
